description: Experience the Refined Elegance of the 2023 Nissan Rogue SVIntroducing the 2023 Nissan Rogue SV, a sophisticated and versatile crossover that seamlessly blends style, performance, and cutting-edge technology. With an impressive EPA-estimated 28 city/35 highway MPG, this Rogue SV offers exceptional efficiency to keep you moving forward with confidence.Step inside the Rogue SV and experience the refined cabin, featuring premium cloth seating, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, and an array of advanced technology. The NissanConnect system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration keeps you seamlessly connected, while the Rear Parking Sensors and Rearview Camera provide added peace of mind when navigating tight spaces.This 2023 Nissan Rogue SV is a certified pre-owned vehicle, meaning it has undergone a rigorous inspection and reconditioning process to ensure it meets the highest standards of quality and reliability. Discover the power and capability of the 2025 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 LT LT1. This rugged and versatile pickup is built to handle any task with ease, from tackling tough terrain to hauling heavy loads. Boasting a robust EcoTec3 5.3L V8 engine, the Silverado 1500 LT LT1 delivers impressive performance, with 355 horsepower and 383 lb-ft of torque, all while maintaining impressive fuel efficiency.

â€¢ 5.3L V8 (EcoTec3) with Dynamic Fuel Management
â€¢ Convenience Package

â€¢ Standard Suspension Package
â€¢ Trailering Package

â€¢ SiriusXM w/360L Trial Subscription
â€¢ Steering Wheel Audio Controls
â€¢ Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control
â€¢ Electric Rear-Window Defogger

The Silverado 1500 LT LT1 is more than just a powerful workhorse, it's a well-equipped and feature-rich vehicle that caters to your every need. From the impressive 12.3" multicolor reconfigurable digital display to the seamless integration of Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, this truck is designed to keep you connected and in control. The Silverado's advanced safety features, including Automatic Emergency Braking, Forward Collision Alert, and Lane Keep Assist, provide you with the confidence and peace of mind you deserve.

Elevate your driving experience with the convenience and comfort of the Silverado 1500 LT LT1. Enjoy the warmth of the heated steering wheel and seats, as well as the versatility of the 60/40 folding rear bench seat. The integrated trailer brake controller and hitch guidance make towing a breeze, while the 120-volt bed-mounted power outlet and Wi-Fi hotspot capability ensure you're always ready for any adventure.

Whether you're tackling a job site, hitting the open road, or embarking on a weekend getaway, the 2025 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 LT LT1 is the perfect companion. With its exceptional performance, advanced technology, and impressive array of features, this truck is poised to exceed your expectations and elevate your driving experience.

Experience the unparalleled capabilities of the 2025 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 LT LT1 for yourself. Schedule a test drive today and discover why this truck is the perfect fit for your lifestyle.

Safety is a top priority in the Lexus RX 350, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. description: The 2013 Jeep Wrangler Sport is a rugged and reliable off-road SUV designed for adventure enthusiasts who value performance and durability. This two-door model is equipped with a capable 3.6-liter V6 engine delivering 285 horsepower and 260 lb-ft of torque, paired with either a manual or automatic transmission, making it ideal for both highway cruising and trailblazing. Standard four-wheel drive ensures confident handling in various driving conditions, from rocky terrain to snow-covered roads. The exterior maintains the iconic Jeep styling with bold lines, a seven-slot grille, and removable doors and roof for an open-air driving experience. This particular model includes factory-installed fog lights, improving visibility during inclement weather or during nighttime off-road excursions. Adding to its versatility, this 2013 Wrangler Sport also comes with a tow package, increasing its functionality for those who enjoy outdoor recreation or need to transport equipment. The tow package enables the Wrangler to haul light trailers, boats, or other gear with ease and confidence. Inside, the interior is built for durability with weather-resistant materials and intuitive controls. Seating for four and ample cargo space in the rear make it practical for both daily driving and weekend trips. Whether you're heading into the wilderness or making a short city commute, the 2013 Jeep Wrangler Sport offers a unique blend of rugged adventure and everyday functionality, with added features that enhance its performance, safety, and convenience.

description: . Our 2016 Audi Q5 3.0 TDI Premium Plus quattro in stunning Blue provides exceptional sophistication and versatility. Powered by a TurboCharged 3.0 Liter V6 Diesel delivering 240hp tethered to an 8 Speed Automatic transmission to send you to 60 in 6.5 seconds and on to 130mph. Our All Wheel Drive luxury crossover offers up to 30mpg on the road, a smooth, comfortable ride, and eye-catching styling accented by a panoramic sunroof, HID headlamps, LED daytime running lights, and distinctive S Line bumpers, side skirts, and split-spoke alloy wheels. Our Q5 Premium Plus cabin offers heated power leather front seats with driver-seat memory, keeping you comfortable on a long drive while you appreciate niceties such as a multi-function steering wheel, auto-dimming interior/exterior mirrors, keyless entry/ignition, a power liftgate, and tri-zone automatic climate control. The infotainment system also features Navigation, satellite radio, an SD card reader, a USB input with iPod integration, and concert-quality audio for your entertainment needs. Our Audi includes various safety technologies to help keep you and your passengers out of harm's way. Rain-sensing wipers, ABS, advanced airbags, tire-pressure monitoring, and stability/traction control are just a few of the systems on hand for your peace of mind. Our Q5 3.0 TDI Premium Plus quattro is ready to enhance your drive, so Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your LSM Cars Test Drive Towards Ownership! . description: The 2017 Ford F-250 Super Duty Lariat is a heavy-duty pickup that expertly combines rugged capability with luxury and advanced technology. This particular model comes equipped with a powerful array of features, including leather luxury captain's chairs with a center console, cooled front seats, premium audio, and a voice-activated navigation system. It also supports Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, ensuring seamless smartphone integration for navigation, music, and hands-free communications. The Lariat Value Package adds even more comfort and convenience, while the Universal Garage Door Opener and Remote Vehicle Start make everyday use easier. The Blind Spot Information System with Cross-Traffic Alert and rear CHMSL camera enhances safety, especially when towing or maneuvering in tight spaces. Visually striking in its Ruby Red Metallic Tinted Clearcoat paint, this F-250 sits on 20-inch bright machined cast aluminum wheels wrapped in LT275/65R20E OWL all-terrain tires, perfect for off-road adventures. The FX4 Off-Road Package adds skid plates and off-road tuned shocks for enhanced durability and capability. Additional practical enhancements include 5-inch chrome tubular running boards for easy access, a 6.8-foot short bed with LED box lighting, tailgate step, and an engine block heater. The 3.55 electronic locking axle ratio enhances towing performance, and factory-installed upfitter switches allow for easy customization. Built for all 50 states, this Super Duty is designed to tackle demanding jobs while delivering a premium driving experience, both on and off the road.

Discover the exceptional 2024 GMC Canyon AT4X, a rugged and capable off-road companion that's ready to elevate your driving experience. This remarkable vehicle combines bold styling, advanced technology, and uncompromising performance to deliver a truly remarkable driving experience.

Highlighted features include:
â€¢ Premium 7-Speaker Bose Sound System
â€¢ Dual-Zone Automatic Air Conditioning
â€¢ Heads-Up Display
â€¢ Memory seat
â€¢ Remote Vehicle Starter System
â€¢ Automatic Emergency Braking
â€¢ Front Pedestrian & Bicyclist Braking
â€¢ Power Inner Sliding Glass Sunroof with Manual Shade

â€¢ Adaptive Cruise Control
â€¢ Canyon Pro Safety

Equipped with a potent 2.7L I4 Turbocharged engine delivering 310 horsepower and an 8-speed automatic transmission, the 2024 GMC Canyon AT4X provides the perfect blend of power and efficiency. Its 4WD capabilities, coupled with the driver-selectable full-locking front and rear differentials, ensure you can tackle any terrain with confidence.

Beyond its impressive performance, this Canyon AT4X offers a wealth of premium features designed to enhance your driving experience. The spacious and well-appointed cabin features perforated leather-appointed seating, a premium Bose sound system, and a large 11.3-inch infotainment display with wireless connectivity. The power-sliding rear window and spray-on bedliner add both functionality and convenience to the truck's versatile design.

Safety is also a top priority, with advanced driver assistance technologies such as Automatic Emergency Braking, Forward Collision Alert, and Lane Keep Assist with Lane Departure Warning keeping you and your passengers secure on the road.

Whether you're navigating the urban jungle or exploring the great outdoors, the 2024 GMC Canyon AT4X is the perfect companion. Its rugged capability, premium features, and exceptional driving dynamics make it a standout in the midsize truck segment. We invite you to experience the power and capability of this remarkable vehicle firsthand. Schedule a test drive today and discover the difference the 2024 GMC Canyon AT4X can make in your driving experience.

Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.

description:
Discover the ultimate off-road companion in the 2023 Toyota Tacoma TRD Off-Road V6. This rugged and capable truck is ready to take on any adventure, whether you're conquering the trails or navigating the daily commute.

Boasting a powerful 3.5L V6 engine paired with a 6-speed transmission and 4-wheel drive, the Tacoma TRD Off-Road delivers exceptional performance and versatility. Standout features include:

â€¢ Front dual zone A/C
â€¢ Remote keyless entry
â€¢ Traction control
â€¢ ABS brakes
â€¢ Low tire pressure warning
â€¢ Electronic Stability Control
â€¢ Heated door mirrors
â€¢ Illuminated entry
â€¢ Alloy wheels

This Tacoma is also equipped with a host of advanced technologies, including Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, and a rearview camera, ensuring you stay connected and confident on the road.

With just 33,513 miles on the odometer, this Tacoma is a certified pre-owned vehicle, meaning it has been thoroughly inspected and comes with a comprehensive warranty for your peace of mind. You can trust that this truck has been meticulously maintained and is ready to take you wherever the road (or trail) may lead.

Combining rugged capability, modern amenities, and the reliability of the Toyota nameplate, the 2023 Tacoma TRD Off-Road V6 is the ultimate adventure-ready vehicle. Experience the power and versatility for yourself by scheduling a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by this exceptional truck.

The Tacoma's impressive fuel efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 19 city/24 highway MPG, means you can explore the great outdoors without constantly stopping for gas. And with its spacious and well-appointed interior, you'll enjoy the journey as much as the destination.

Whether you're an avid off-roader, a weekend warrior, or simply seeking a capable and reliable truck, the 2023 Toyota Tacoma TRD Off-Road V6 is the perfect choice. Visit our showroom today and let us help you discover the perfect vehicle to suit your lifestyle and needs.

But the true allure of this Yukon lies in its exceptional capabilities and premium amenities. Equipped with a powerful EcoTec3 5.3L V8 engine and a smooth-shifting 10-speed automatic transmission, this 4WD beast delivers impressive performance and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 15 city/20 highway MPG.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like Forward Collision Alert, Lane Keep Assist, and the Safety Alert Seat keeping you and your loved ones secure on the road. Heated and ventilated front seats, along with heated second-row outboard seats, ensure everyone rides in comfort.

Our business model is simple, we treat each and every customer the same way we would expect to be treated. Whether you're looking for a new or pre-owned car, Sea Breeze Ford can help!Each of our pre-owned cars and trucks undergoes the same 179 point inspection that Ford Motor Company requires for the Blue Advantage certification program, whether it is Gold Certified, Blue Certified or Value priced.You can purchase the vehicle with the Peace of Mind knowing that a Ford Factory trained technician has inspected the vehicle and brought it up to factory standards.In addition to our quality vehicles, we offer a transparent transaction, the price you see is the price of the vehicle. Unlike many dealerships we do not have any hidden fees such as an "Internet Buying Fee", "Prep/Delivery fee", "Paint Protection Fee", "Nitrogen in the Tires fee etc. Our $590 Dealer Doc Fee is the only fee we charge and is amongst the lowest in the state.If you want a quality pre-owned vehicle at a great price, in a friendly NO-PRESSURE environment, come to Seabreeze Ford, Where we offer Miles of Smiles!Our new inventory is packed with brand-new Ford cars, trucks, SUVs, and vans to match every driver's wants and needs. From tough trucks like the Ford F-150 and Ford Super Duty and sporty sedans like the Ford Mustang to spacious SUVs and work vans like the Ford Explorer, Ford Edge, and Ford Transit, we have something for every driver to enjoy. description: The 2009 Dodge Ram 2500 Laramie Mega Cab is a powerful and refined heavy-duty pickup that delivers both performance and comfort. With its bold exterior styling and rugged capability, this truck stands out on the road and at the worksite. Equipped with fog lights, it provides better visibility during inclement weather or early morning starts. The Mega Cab configuration offers expansive rear-seat legroom, making it a great choice for families, work crews, or anyone who needs additional interior space without compromising utility. Known for its towing power and durability, this Ram 2500 Laramie is as capable pulling heavy loads as it is navigating daily errands, making it a versatile choice for drivers who demand toughness and comfort in one package.----Inside, the Laramie trim delivers a premium experience with a host of upscale features. The cabin is outfitted with leather seats that enhance not only the look but the overall comfort of the driving experience. Heated front seats add a touch of luxury, especially in cold climates, while the power-adjustable front seats allow for customized comfort with ease. Entertainment and connectivity are handled by a premium audio system, and Bluetooth integration lets you stay connected on the move. Whether you're on a long highway drive or navigating city streets, the blend of comfort, technology, and raw power in this 2009 Dodge Ram 2500 Laramie Mega Cab ensures every ride is enjoyable and confident.

Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.

Convenience
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
Safety and Security
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

# **2014 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 LT 100,043 miles $18,000**

This 2014 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 LT delivers the perfect balance of capability, comfort, and reliability. Finished in a sleek Gray exterior over a BLACK interior, this Double Cab 4WD model is built to tackle work duties and weekend adventures with equal confidence. With Chevys well-regarded EcoTec3 V8 under the hood and a smooth 6-speed automatic transmission, it offers strong performance and proven durability.

## **Key Features**

* **Performance:** Powerful **EcoTec3 5.3L V8 Flex Fuel** engine
* **Drivetrain & Capability:** **4WD** system for traction and control in all conditions
* **Transmission:** **6-Speed Automatic Electronic with Overdrive** for smooth shifting
* **Interior Comfort:** Spacious **4D Double Cab** with durable **BLACK** seating
* **Technology:** Standard infotainment and driver convenience features
* **Safety:** Stability control, advanced braking support, and airbags
* **Utility:** Generous bed space and towing capability, ideal for work or recreation

## **Why It Stands Out**

With **100,043 miles**, this Silverado LT combines dependable V8 performance, 4WD versatility, and the comfort of a Double Cab configuration. Its proven reliability and practical features make it a strong value for anyone seeking a capable and durable full-size truck.

**Price:** $18,000

description:
The 2021 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 Crew Cab LT RWD in Black is a full-size pickup truck that blends everyday usability with dependable capability and a strong, confident presence. Its Black exterior color gives the Silverado a sleek and classic lookdeep and timeless, it highlights the trucks bold grille, rugged stance, and smooth body lines. Whether parked at a job site, in a driveway, or cruising down the highway, the rich black finish helps the Silverado look commanding and purposeful without being flashy.

Under the hood, the 2021 Silverado 1500 LT delivers robust and reliable performance that feels well-suited for a variety of driving needs. Whether youre commuting to work, hauling gear to the job site, or towing when needed, this trucks powertrain provides confident acceleration and dependable strength. In rear-wheel-drive configuration, the Silverado offers responsive performance on paved roads with a balanced and composed driving feel thats comfortable for daily driving and practical duties alike.

Step inside, and youll find a spacious and thoughtfully designed cabin that focuses on comfort, convenience, and everyday usability. The Crew Cab layout provides generous legroom and headroom in both the front and rear seats, making it a comfortable choice for adults and passengers of all ages. The seats are supportive and designed to make long rides and daily errands equally comfortable. With plenty of space for passengers and storage compartments in the cabin, the Silverado makes it easy to stay organized on the go.

The LT trim adds a number of features that enhance the overall driving experience. The dashboard is intuitive and driver-friendly, with easy-to-reach controls and a clean design that helps keep your focus on the road. A user-friendly infotainment system provides access to music, apps, and other connected features, and with available smartphone integration like Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, you can seamlessly use your favorite navigation tools and media while driving. Bluetooth connectivity and USB ports help keep devices paired and charged for every journey.

Cargo capability is a major strength of the Silverado. The truck bed offers plenty of space for tools, equipment, furniture, or other large items you need to move. Whether youre loading lumber, outdoor gear, or large boxes, the beds capacity and sturdy construction make everyday hauling feel straightforward and reliable. Tie-down points and available bed accessories add versatility so you can secure your load with confidence.

Safety is also an important part of the 2021 Silverados design. A range of standard safety features helps provide peace of mind on the road. Components like multiple airbags, stability and traction control, and rearview camera systems work together to support driver awareness and help provide protection in a variety of driving situations. Available driver-assist technologies further enhance confidence behind the wheel and help support safer operation in traffic, parking lots, and on longer trips.

Overall, the 2021 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 Crew Cab LT RWD in Black offers a strong blend of reliable performance, everyday comfort, modern technology, and practical capability. Its commanding color, spacious interior, and thoughtful features make it a versatile choice for drivers who want a full-size pickup truck thats ready for daily use, weekend projects, and everything in between.

Experience the ultimate in power, comfort, and technology with this stunning 2018 Ram 1500 Laramie. Boasting a powerful HEMI 5.7L V8 engine, this capable 4x4 truck delivers exceptional performance and fuel efficiency, with an impressive 15 city and 21 highway MPG.

â€¢ 172 Point Safety Inspection
â€¢ Convenience Group
â€¢ Quick Order Package 27H Laramie
â€¢ Trailer Tow Mirrors & Brake Group
â€¢ 1-Yr SiriusXM Guardian Trial

Slip behind the wheel and experience the unparalleled luxury of the Laramie trim. Sink into the plush, heated and ventilated leather seats, and let the 8.4-inch Uconnect touchscreen infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto connectivity keep you connected and entertained. The premium 10-speaker audio system will elevate your driving experience, while the power sunroof and remote start system add an extra touch of convenience.

Safety is paramount, and this Ram 1500 Laramie delivers with features like forward collision warning, lane departure warning, and the ParkView rear backup camera. You'll also enjoy the peace of mind that comes with the SiriusXM Guardian emergency communication system.

Whether you're hauling a trailer, navigating the city, or embarking on a long-distance adventure, this 2018 Ram 1500 Laramie is the perfect companion. Its impressive towing capacity, advanced 4x4 system, and premium amenities make it a true standout in the full-size truck segment.

Discover the perfect blend of power, capability, and refinement with this exceptional 2018 Ram 1500 Laramie. Visit our showroom today to experience it for yourself and take the first step towards owning this exceptional vehicle.

All prices include Alpine Down Payment Assistance of $1,000 financing credit and $689.50 dealer and handling.

Discover the power and capability of the 2022 Ram 1500 Big Horn/Lone Star. This rugged and versatile pickup is the perfect companion for your adventures, whether you're tackling tough jobs or exploring the great outdoors.

â€¢ 5.7L HEMI V8 engine with Multi-Displacement System and Variable Valve Timing
â€¢ Big Horn Level 1 Equipment Group with advanced technology features
â€¢ Remote Start System for added convenience
â€¢ Black, deluxe cloth bucket seats with power-adjustable driver's seat

The 2022 Ram 1500 Big Horn/Lone Star is built to impress. Its bold, muscular design commands attention, while the 4-wheel drive system and powerful HEMI engine deliver the performance you need to conquer any terrain. Inside, the spacious and well-appointed cabin offers the latest in-vehicle technology, including an 8.4-inch touchscreen display, Apple CarPlay, and a 4G LTE Wi-Fi hotspot.

Elevate your driving experience with the Big Horn Level 1 Equipment Group, which includes a wealth of premium features. Enjoy the convenience of remote start, the added visibility of front fog lights, and the enhanced safety of ParkView Rear Back-Up Camera. Stay connected with integrated voice command, Bluetooth, and SiriusXM satellite radio.

Comfort and convenience are at the forefront of this exceptional truck. The power-adjustable driver's seat and tilt/telescoping steering wheel allow you to find your perfect driving position, while the dual-zone automatic climate control keeps you and your passengers comfortable.

Whether you're hauling heavy loads, navigating rough terrain, or simply enjoying the open road, the 2022 Ram 1500 Big Horn/Lone Star is the perfect companion. Experience the power, capability, and technology that make this truck a standout in its class.

Don't miss your chance to make this Ram 1500 your own. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate the impressive features and capabilities of this exceptional vehicle.

description: Get ready to dominate the road in this striking 2021 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 RST Rally Edition. Dressed in a crisp Summit White with blacked-out accents, this truck is designed for those who want their pickup to have a sporty, street-inspired edge. Under the hood, the powerful 5.3L V8 engine delivers the muscle you need for heavy-duty tasks while providing a smooth, responsive drive that makes every trip enjoyable. With a Clean CARFAX, this 4WD Crew Cab is as reliable as it is bold.The Rally Edition AdvantageThe Rally Edition takes the already athletic RST trim to the next level. You'll stand out from the crowd with black hood and tailgate stripes, black badging, and a black exhaust tip. This truck rolls on massive 22" High Gloss Black wheels and features 4" Black Round Assist Steps, making it easy to climb in and out while adding to its aggressive stance. Its a truck that looks just as good parked at a stadium as it does pulling a trailer through the hills.A Cabin Built for Your Busy LifeInside, the Silverado RST offers a perfect mix of comfort and functionality. The heated front bucket seats and heated steering wheel keep you warm on chilly mornings, while the dual-zone automatic climate control ensures everyone stays comfortable. With the Convenience Package w/ Bucket Seats, you get a floor-mounted center console and plenty of storage options. Plus, with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration and a 4G LTE Wi-Fi Hotspot, you're always connected to your world.Towing and Utility Made SimpleWhether you're hauling a boat to the lake or gear to the job site, this Silverado is ready to work. It comes equipped with the Trailering Package, an Integrated Trailer Brake Controller, and Hitch Guidance to take the stress out of hitching up. The bed is protected by a Chevytec Spray-On Black Bedliner and features LED cargo area lighting and an EZ Lift Power Lock & Release Tailgate, making loading and unloading easier than ever, even after the sun goes down.Experience the Superior DifferenceAt the Superior Pre-Owned Superstore of Bentonville, we believe car buying should be just as exciting as the vehicle you're taking home. This Silverado RST has been meticulously cleaned, professionally serviced, and is ready for its next owner to drive away with a smile. Let us show you why we've won the trust of Arkansas drivers for 30 years by offering a faster, simpler, and more transparent experience. Visit us at http://www.bentonvillepreowned.com or call today!Faster. Simpler. More Transparent. Superior Automotive Group has helped thousands of customers find the right car by leveraging one of Arkansas' largest selections of new and pre-owned vehicles at unparalleled prices. Yet, it's our extra-mile customer service and uncommonly candid and respectful staff that have won the trust and loyalty of Arkansas drivers for 30 years. Come visit one of our Superior dealerships today and let us exceed your expectations.

description:
Experience the perfect blend of style and performance with this stunning 2019 Volkswagen Beetle Convertible 2.0T SE. This captivating convertible is ready to elevate your driving experience and turn heads wherever you go.

Boasting a sleek Gray exterior, this Beetle Convertible is equipped with a host of premium features that set it apart from the crowd. The vehicle's custom-tailored enhancements include - VW CARE, a Volkswagen prepaid scheduled maintenance contract with 10,000-mile and 20,000-mile servicing, a set of Chrome Exhaust Tips, the Monster Mats w/Logo Rubber Mat Kit, and a comprehensive Roadside Assistance Kit to ensure your peace of mind on the road.

Under the hood, the Beetle Convertible is powered by a robust 2.0L TSI engine, paired with a smooth-shifting 6-Speed Automatic with Tiptronic transmission. This powertrain delivers an impressive blend of efficiency and performance, with an EPA-estimated 26 MPG in the city and 33 MPG on the highway.

Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a well-appointed interior that combines style and comfort. The V-Tex Leatherette Seating Surfaces provide a luxurious touch, while the Heated Front Comfort Seats ensure you and your passengers stay cozy, even on the chilliest days. The Leather Shift Knob and Leather Steering Wheel add a refined touch, while the Tilt and Telescoping Steering Wheel allows you to find the perfect driving position.

Technology features abound, with an 8-Speaker audio system, CD player, Radio Data System, and Steering Wheel-Mounted Audio Controls, keeping you connected and entertained on the road. The Rear View Camera and Integrated Rear Spoiler further enhance the Beetle Convertible's functionality and style.

This exceptional Volkswagen Beetle Convertible is a true standout in its class, blending timeless design, impressive performance, and a wealth of premium features. Experience the joy of open-air driving and discover the perfect balance of sophistication and fun. Visit our showroom today to take this captivating convertible for a test drive and make it your own.

description: The 2020 Kia Soul GT-Line offers a bold blend of sporty styling and advanced technology, making it a standout option in the compact crossover segment. Designed with performance-inspired touches, the GT-Line model features sleek body lines, unique front and rear fascia, and 18-inch alloy wheels that emphasize its athletic flair. Under the hood, it delivers a responsive drive, while inside, drivers will enjoy a comfortable and high-tech cabin outfitted with premium leather seats and a sporty D-shaped steering wheel. The addition of a Head-Up Display keeps essential driving information in the driver's line of sight, enhancing focus and safety during every journey. Packed with intelligent driver-assistance features, the 2020 Kia Soul GT-Line doesn't compromise on safety or convenience. Adaptive Cruise Control automatically adjusts speed to maintain a safe distance from vehicles ahead, while Lane Keep Assist gently corrects steering to help the vehicle stay centered in its lane. Forward Collision Warning provides added security with alerts to help the driver avoid potential accidents. For those who appreciate top-tier entertainment, the premium audio system delivers crisp, immersive sound throughout the cabin, elevating every trip. Whether navigating city streets or cruising on the highway, the 2020 Soul GT-Line expertly combines style, comfort, and cutting-edge features to meet the needs of modern drivers.

description: The 2020 Ford F-150 XLT Long Bed is a versatile and reliable full-size pickup truck designed to handle demanding workloads while offering modern convenience and comfort. This particular model features the sought-after long bed configuration, giving it increased cargo space and making it well-suited for hauling tools, building materials, or recreational gear. Under the hood, the F-150 offers strong engine options, delivering responsive power and dependable performance whether you're on the job site or the open road. Its rugged build quality and high towing capacity make it a favorite among drivers who need a truck that works as hard as they do. In addition to its work-ready capabilities, this F-150 XLT comes equipped with a range of modern tech features for safety and connectivity. The integrated Wi-Fi hotspot keeps you connected wherever the road takes you, while both Apple CarPlay and Android Auto allow seamless smartphone integration for music, calls, navigation, and more. Bluetooth functionality enables hands-free communication, and the backup camera offers added ease and security when reversing or parking. Collision Warning helps enhance driver awareness and safety, providing alerts in potentially hazardous situations. Altogether, this 2020 Ford F-150 XLT Long Bed blends functionality and technology, making it a smart choice for anyone in need of a truck that delivers performance, spaciousness, and connectivity in one dependable package.

description: The 2020 Ram 1500 Limited expertly blends luxury, performance, and cutting-edge technology for a premium driving experience. Powered by the 5.7L HEMI V8 engine with eTorque, this truck produces a robust 395 hp and 410 lb-ft of torque, ideal for heavy-duty performance and smooth highway cruising. Paired with the 3.92 axle ratio and Anti-Spin Rear Differential, it delivers exceptional towing capabilities, especially when combined with the factory-installed Trailer Brake Controller. The Quick Order Package 27M and Protection Group add functional enhancements for durability and convenience, while the Body Color Bumper Group provides a sleek, unified exterior design, all dressed in a striking Delmonico Red Pearl Coat Paint. Inside, the 2020 Ram 1500 Limited offers a refined and technologically advanced cabin. The Premium Leather-Trimmed Bucket Seats provide supreme comfort for long drives, and the Limited Level 1 Equipment Group introduces high-end features like Adaptive Cruise Control, Lane Keep Assist, and a high-fidelity Premium Audio system. Connectivity is seamless with the built-in Wi-Fi Hotspot, keeping you connected on the go. The Dual-Pane Panoramic Sunroof floods the cabin with natural light, enhancing the already spacious and luxurious atmosphere. With its blend of rugged capability and upscale features, this Ram 1500 Limited is a standout choice for those who demand both performance and premium amenities from their truck.

The 2023 Ford F-150 Lariat in Star White Metallic Tri-Coat combines advanced technology, rugged capability, and premium comfort. Powered by the 3.5L PowerBoost Full-Hybrid V6, this 4WD truck delivers impressive performance, efficiency, and towing capability, making it perfect for work or adventure. The interior is packed with luxury and convenience features, including heated and ventilated front seats, 2nd-row heated seats, a twin-panel moonroof, wireless charging pad, in-vehicle safe by Console Vault, and the B&O Unleashed Sound System by Bang & Olufsen. Exterior features like 20" Chrome-Like PVD wheels, accent-color angular step bars, and body-color bumpers combine style and functionality, while the LED lighting package enhances visibility and presence.

Designed for capability, this F-150 includes the Max Trailer Tow Package, Pro Trailer Backup Assist, Class IV Trailer Hitch Receiver, Integrated Trailer Brake Controller, and a 3.73 electronic locking axle ratio, along with a GVWR of 7,350 lbs, allowing you to tackle heavy-duty towing and hauling with confidence. Safety and driver-assist features such as Ford Co-Pilot360 Assist 2.0, Intelligent Adaptive Cruise Control with Stop & Go, Evasive Steering Assist, Intersection Assist, and a 360-degree camera elevate the driving experience. Recently arrived, this truck comes with a Ford Gold Certified warranty, 172-point inspection, and additional benefits including FordPass Rewards points, roadside assistance, and a transferable powertrain warranty, making it a premium, fully-equipped, and reliable choice for its next owner.

description: The 2017 Toyota Tacoma SR5 Long Bed is a rugged and reliable midsize pickup designed to deliver strong performance and advanced technology, making it ideal for both work and everyday driving. This particular model comes equipped with several desirable features that enhance convenience and safety, including a user-friendly navigation system to keep you on the right track, a backup camera that provides clear visibility when reversing, and Bluetooth connectivity for hands-free calling and audio streaming. The long bed configuration offers increased cargo space, making it easier to haul tools, gear, or suppliesâ€”perfect for those who value utility and functionality in their truck. Inside the cabin, the 2017 Tacoma SR5 Long Bed combines durability with modern tech comforts. Wireless phone charging keeps your devices powered without the clutter of cords, while push-button start adds a level of convenience typically found in more premium vehicles. Side impact airbags provide added peace of mind, enhancing occupant protection in the event of a collision. The interior layout is intuitive and built with quality materials, making it a comfortable place to spend time whether you're commuting, heading to a job site, or exploring off-road trails. With its blend of toughness, technology, and safety, this Tacoma SR5 Long Bed model remains a popular choice for drivers who need a truck that's as dependable as it is versatile.

Discover the perfect family companion in the 2023 Toyota Highlander L. This versatile SUV offers a compelling blend of style, performance, and advanced technology, making it an exceptional choice for your next vehicle.

â€¢ Powerful 2.4L I4 turbocharged engine delivering 265 horsepower
â€¢ Efficient all-wheel-drive system for confident handling in any conditions
â€¢ Impressive fuel economy ratings of 21 MPG in the city and 28 MPG on the highway

The Highlander L comes equipped with an impressive array of features that cater to your every need:

â€¢ 8" Toyota Audio Multimedia system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration
â€¢ Dual-zone automatic climate control for personalized comfort
â€¢ Rearview camera with dynamic guidelines for easy parking and maneuvering
â€¢ Toyota Safety Sense suite of advanced driver-assist technologies

Step into the spacious and well-appointed interior of the Highlander L, where you'll find seating for up to eight passengers and ample cargo space for all your adventures. The split-folding third-row seat and versatile layout provide the flexibility to accommodate your family's needs with ease.

Elevate your driving experience with the Highlander L's smooth and responsive handling, thanks to its four-wheel independent suspension and speed-sensing steering. Whether navigating city streets or embarking on a road trip, this SUV delivers a confident and comfortable ride.

With its sleek and modern exterior design, the Highlander L exudes a sense of sophistication that is sure to turn heads. The 18-inch alloy wheels and body-color bumpers lend a touch of refinement, while the power-adjustable and heated side mirrors ensure convenience and visibility.

Discover the perfect balance of practicality, performance, and style in the 2023 Toyota Highlander L. Visit our showroom today and experience the exceptional value and peace of mind that this exceptional SUV has to offer.

2019 MERCEDES-BENZ SPRINTER 2500 CONVERSION

LUXURY SPRINTER VAN CONVERSION, PREMIUM PACKAGE PLUS, EXTERIOR LIGHTING PACKAGE, AND MORE!

OVERVIEW
Step into first-class luxury on wheels with this customized 2019 Mercedes-Benz Sprinter 2500, offering the perfect blend of professional-grade utility and upscale passenger comfort. Powered by a 3.0L V6 Turbo Diesel engine, this Sprinter 2500 delivers smooth torque, quiet operation, and excellent long-distance fuel efficiency. Rear-wheel drive and a 7-speed automatic transmission provide confident handling and towing capability, while the Premium Plus Package adds peace of mind with advanced driver-assistance features like Blind Spot Assist, Collision Prevention Assist, and Lane Keeping Assist. Inside, this van sets a new standard for rear passenger comfort. Custom captain's chairs in premium leather feature multi-way adjustment and heating. Soft-touch surfaces, ambient lighting, and elegant contrast stitching elevate the cabin's ambiance. The rear seating area includes multiple USB ports, an integrated TV, and woodgrain trim, offering both productivity and relaxation on the go. Whether you're transporting VIP clients, planning cross-country travel, or seeking the ultimate mobile office, this fully built-out Sprinter delivers refinement, safety, and versatility in one commanding package.

description: Experience the ultimate in spacious comfort and versatility with this sleek Black 2018 Ford Transit Passenger Wagon. Boasting a powerful 3.7L Ti-VCT V6 engine with SEIC capability, this beauty is ready to take on any road trip adventure you have in mind. With rear-wheel drive and a 3.73 axle ratio, you can expect a smooth and responsive driving experience every time you hit the road.Step inside and you'll find a spacious interior with plenty of seating for your passengers. The 4-way passenger seat and manual tilt/telescoping steering column ensure that everyone rides in comfort, while the HVAC system keeps the cabin at the perfect temperature no matter the weather outside. With ample storage space and multiple power outlets, you'll have everything you need for a long journey ahead.Safety is a top priority with this Ford Transit, featuring dual stage driver and passenger front airbags, side impact beams, and a back-up camera to help you navigate with ease. The Low Tire Pressure Warning system and airbag occupancy sensor provide added peace of mind for you and your passengers on every trip.This 2018 Ford Transit Passenger Wagon comes with a Carfax report, so you can purchase with confidence knowing the vehicle's history. Whether you're transporting a large group of friends or family, this Transit has the space and comfort you need for a memorable journey. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a stylish and versatile vehicle that's perfect for all your travel needs. Visit Texano Auto Sales online at www.TexanoAutoSales.com to see more pictures of this vehicle or call us at 678-450- 0501 today to schedule your test drive. description:
Vehicle Details
Looking for a reliable work van with low miles and the best price in Roanoke VA? This 2020 Ford Transit Van T-250 Med Roof Slide Base is the ideal choice. With just 27,506 miles, this Transit delivers dependable performance from its V6 3.5L Gasoline/E85 engine and rear-wheel drive, offering strong towing and hauling capability for contractors, delivery operations, or small business owners. This Transit comes with a CARFAX Clean Report and is a CARFAX 1-Owner vehicle, giving you extra confidence in its maintenance history and condition. Practical features include Hands Free Bluetooth for safer calls and music streaming while on the road, plus a Back-Up Camera to simplify parking and maneuvering this medium-roof van in tight job sites or urban streets. The medium roof provides versatile cargo space and easy access through the sliding side door, making cargo loading and customizing the interior simple. Designed for commercial reliability, this Transit T-250 balances utility and comfort with a roomy driver area and straightforward controls you can count on day after day. Located in Roanoke VA, this low-mileage Transit is competitively priced to move quickly. If you want a work-ready van backed by a clean CARFAX and a single-owner history, this 2020 Ford Transit T-250 Med Roof Slide Base is an outstanding value. Contact us to schedule a test drive and secure the best price today.

Equipment
Our dealership has already run the CARFAX report and it is clean. A clean CARFAX is a great asset for resale value in the future. The vehicle features a hands-free Bluetooth phone system. See what's behind you with the back up camera on it. Good News! This certified CARFAX 1-owner vehicle has only had one owner before you. Maintaining a stable interior temperature in this 2020 Ford Transit Van T-250 Med Roof Slide is easy with the climate control system. This model is rear wheel drive. The Ford Transit Van has a V6, 3.5L high output engine. This model embodies class and sophistication with its refined white exterior. This vehicle has an automatic transmission. Electronic Stability Control is one of many advanced safety features on this 2020 Ford Transit Van T-250 Med Roof Slide. Easily set your speed in this 3/4 ton van with a state of the art cruise control system. Increase or decrease velocity with the touch of a button.

Packages
Exterior Upgrade Package: Wiper Activated Headlamps, Three Bar Grill with Chrome Surround, 16" Steel Wheels with Full Silver Cover, Chrome-Trimmed Halogen Headlamps. Order Code 101A: AM/FM Stereo, 10-Speed Automatic Transmission with OD and SelectShift, Vinyl Front Bucket Seats, 3.5L PFDi V6 Flex-Fuel Engine, Dark Palazzo Gray Vinyl Bucket Seats, 235/65R16C 121/119 R AS BSW Tires, 9. 070 lbs GVWR. Heavy-Duty Trailer Tow Package: Frame Mounted Hitch Receiver, Tow/Haul Mode with Trailer Wiring Provisions. Load Area Protection Package. 3.73 Limited-Slip Axle Ratio. Cruise Control with Adjustable Speed Limiting Device (ASLD). Tow/Haul Mode with Trailer Wiring Provisions. Front and Rear Vinyl Floor Covering. Front Fog Lamps. 16" Steel Wheels with Full Silver Cover. Wiper Activated Headlamps. **Equipment listed is based on original vehicle build and subject to change. Please confirm the accuracy of the included equipment by calling the dealer prior to purchase.**

description:
This 2020 Ford Transit-350 XLT 15-Passenger Seats is a versatile and well-equipped vehicle that offers exceptional value and functionality. With its spacious interior, robust performance, and comprehensive list of features, this Transit-350 is the perfect choice for those seeking a reliable and adaptable transportation solution.

- 15-Passenger Seats
- 8 Speakers (4 Front/4 Rear)
- Air Conditioning
- Power Steering
- Power Windows
- Remote Keyless Entry
- Traction Control
- ABS Brakes
- Dual Front Impact Airbags
- Dual Front Side Impact Airbags
- Emergency Communication System: 911 Assist
- Exterior Parking Camera Rear
- Rear Parking Sensors
- Auto High-beam Headlights
- Front Fog Lamps

Powered by a robust V6 engine paired with a 10-Speed Automatic transmission with Overdrive, this Transit-350 delivers a smooth and responsive driving experience. The rear-wheel-drive configuration provides excellent stability and control, making it ideal for a variety of applications, from passenger transport to light commercial use.

The spacious interior of the Transit-350 offers ample seating for up to 15 passengers, ensuring that you can comfortably accommodate your family, friends, or colleagues. The split-bench third-row seat and the 4th-Row Bench Seat provide versatile seating options, allowing you to easily adapt the cabin to your specific needs.

In addition to its impressive passenger capacity, the Transit-350 is also equipped with a host of advanced features that enhance your driving experience. The SYNC 3 infotainment system with AM/FM radio keeps you connected and entertained, while the Rear Parking Sensors and Exterior Parking Camera Rear provide added confidence and convenience when maneuvering in tight spaces.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, and the Emergency Communication System: 911 Assist, ensuring that you and your passengers are well-protected.

Excellent Finance Options Available. We offer transparent, tailored financing to fit your budget.

Buy with Confidence: We've proudly served Union for over 50 years with a trusted reputation for professionalism and customer satisfaction.

Contact Us Today to schedule a test drive or get a personalized quote.

The Ford Transit-350 XLT offers unparalleled utility and functionality. With its spacious 15-passenger seating configuration, you can easily accommodate large groups or transport your entire crew with ease. description:
This 2022 Mercedes-Benz Sprinter 2500 Crew Van finished in Graphite Gray offers exceptional versatility, comfort, and capability for both work and passenger transport. Configured with a high roof and crew van layout, it provides generous interior space with seating for passengers while maintaining ample cargo capacity.

This Sprinter is well equipped with multiple comfort packages, heated and power-adjustable front seats, lumbar support, upgraded interior trim, and durable Artico man-made leather upholstery. The MBUX multimedia system with navigation, SiriusXM, smartphone tray, live traffic pre-installation, and color instrument cluster keep the cabin modern and connected.

Driver assistance features include Active Lane Keeping Assist, Attention Assist, rain-sensing wipers, and the Parking Package with 360-degree camera for added confidence and ease of maneuvering. Practical upgrades such as wood flooring with D-rings, full side wall paneling, sliding side door, rear doors opening to the side wall, and roof rack mounting rails make this Sprinter highly functional for commercial or recreational use.

With a factory trailer hitch rated at 5,000 pounds, all-season tires, and thoughtful utility features throughout, this Sprinter 2500 Crew Van is a capable, comfortable solution for businesses or families needing space, flexibility, and Mercedes-Benz durability.

Experience The Diamond Difference. If you're looking for a vehicle that delivers on performance, utility, comfort, or value, this 2024 Ford Transit 350 XLT may be just the ticket... Vehicle Highlights: Daytime Running Lamps ($45 value)
    Privacy Glass ($500 value)
    • Includes rear cargo door window defogger, and privacy glass.
    SYNC 4 with SiriusXM 360L and HD Radio ($235 value)
    • Includes SYNC 4 with enhanced conversational voice recognition, 12 in. LCD capacitive touchscreen, SiriusXM with 360L, HD radio, connected navigation, Bluetooth, dual USB ports, and automatic temperature control.
    Safety and Security
    • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
    • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
    • Active blind spot system - Protect your blind side. You checked the mirror, looked over your shoulder and still nearly collided with the car next to you. An active blind spot system not only alerts you to the presence of a vehicle to your sides or rear but helps prevent you from making an unsafe lane change. Replace fear and uncertainty with the confidence and safety of the Active blind spot system.
    • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.
    Other Options/Features ENGINE: 3.5L ECOBOOST V6, OXFORD WHITE, DARK PALAZZO GRAY, CLOTH FRONT BUCKET SEATS Why Buy From Diamond Buick GMC? The 2024 Express 2500 Work Van Cargo is more than just a workhorse - it's a trusted partner that will help you get the job done. The front bucket seats with custom cloth trim provide comfortable seating, while the swing-out storage bin in the console offers convenient storage for your essential tools and supplies. The backup camera and power windows and locks add a level of modern convenience that will make your workday easier.

Whether you're hauling heavy cargo or transporting your crew, the 2024 Chevrolet Express 2500 Work Van Cargo is up to the task. (Unsure whether it's aftermarket or not) Why are partitions (AKA bulkheads) so important? Van partitions do more than just block the view or reduce the noise of the cargo. When you install a van partition, you're also taking advantage of these benefits: Partitions save lives: The primary purpose of a partition is to protect the driver and passenger from shifting cargo in the event of a hard stop or accident. Increased driver comfort: A partition helps retain the climate control in the cab rather than escaping to the back. Separate the cargo area: The right partition will help prevent odors, dust, and other materials from coming into the cab. Increased security: Without a partition, one of the easiest routes for a criminal to your tools in the rear is through the cab windows. This is an exceptional one-owner 2024 Ford Transit T-250 cargo van with just 24k original miles. This is easily one of the lowest-mile examples available and it shows in every way. This van is in outstanding condition and has clearly been very well cared for since new.

This is not your typical beat-up cargo van. The paint and body are in excellent condition with no road rash, no dents, no scratches, and not a single rock chip. There is zero rust or corrosion anywhere. The interior is smoke-free and presents like new.

If you are looking to save thousands over buying new while still getting a nearly new van, this is it.

CONDITION

Paint and body are clean, straight, and well preserved
No dents, dings, scratches, or rock chips
Interior is smoke-free and like new

Undercarriage is clean with no rust or corrosion

Digital odometer

Everything works exactly as it should.

WARRANTY AND SERVICE

This Transit is still under the remaining Ford factory warranty, including:

3 years or 36,000 miles bumper to bumper
5 years or 60,000 miles powertrain

It has been fully serviced and inspected and needs absolutely nothing.

THE TYACKE MOTORS STANDARD

You will not find a cleaner, lower-mile Transit.

Multiple Transits in stock, inventory changes daily

Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Blind spot warning - Protect your blind side. You checked the mirror, looked over your shoulder and still nearly collided with the car next to you. Blind spot warning alerts you to the presence of a vehicle to your sides or rear so you know if you're about to make an unsafe lane change. Replace fear and uncertainty with confidence and safety with blind spot warning.
Technology and Telematics

description:
Commanding attention on the road, the 2024 GMC Savana 2500 Work Van is a versatile and capable companion for your business needs. With its impressive 4.3L V6 engine, 8-speed automatic transmission, and rear-wheel drive, this work van delivers the power and performance you require to tackle any job.

â€¢ DRIVER CONVENIENCE PACKAGE: Includes tilt-wheel and cruise control for added comfort and control.
â€¢ CHROME APPEARANCE PACKAGE: Elevates the exterior with chrome front and rear bumpers and a striking chrome grille.
â€¢ CRUISE CONTROL: Allows you to maintain a consistent speed, reducing driver fatigue on long hauls.
â€¢ REAR AND SIDE CARGO DOOR GLASS: Provides visibility and safety when maneuvering in tight spaces.
â€¢ FRONT BUCKET SEATS WITH CUSTOM CLOTH TRIM: Offer exceptional comfort and support for the driver and passenger.
â€¢ BLACK SEAT BELTS: Add a touch of sophistication to the interior.

This Savana 2500 Work Van is equipped with an impressive array of features that enhance both functionality and convenience. The driver and passenger will appreciate the single-zone manual air conditioning, power windows, and tilt steering wheel, while the rear cargo area benefits from the full-length black rubberized-vinyl floor covering and fixed rear door window glass.

Safety is paramount, and this work van delivers with features like dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, electronic stability control, and a rear vision camera. The OnStar and GMC connected services capability provide added peace of mind, ensuring you stay connected and protected on the road.

Elevate your business operations with the 2024 GMC Savana 2500 Work Van. Its exceptional capabilities, thoughtful design, and comprehensive safety features make it the ideal choice for professionals who demand the best. Experience the difference for yourself by scheduling a test drive today.

description: Introducing the luxurious 2025 Cadillac Escalade Sport Platinum, a jewel in the world of SUVs. This stunning model features a striking Crystal White Tricoat exterior that exudes sophistication and style, perfectly complemented by a rich Jet Black interior that combines comfort and elegance. Under the hood, the Escalade is powered by a robust EcoTec3 6.2L V8 gasoline engine, equipped with innovative direct injection and variable valve control technologies. Generating an impressive 420 horsepower, this powerhouse is designed for optimal performance and efficiency, thanks to its cylinder deactivation feature. Experience unparalleled luxury with the Sport Platinum trim, which offers an array of premium features and cutting-edge technology to elevate your driving experience. From its spacious interior, loaded with advanced connectivity options, to its state-of-the-art safety features, every journey feels exceptional-whether you're navigating city streets or hitting the open road. The 2025 Cadillac Escalade Sport Platinum 4WD is more than just a vehicle, it's a statement of excellence and performance. Don't miss your chance to own this remarkable SUV.

description: 2016 Lexus GX 460 -- White Exterior -- 137,122 Miles Step up to full-size luxury and rugged capability with this 2016 Lexus GX 460, finished in a timeless white exterior. Known for its refined craftsmanship, smooth V8 power, and true off-road capability, the GX 460 is one of the most versatile luxury SUVs on the road. With 137,122 miles, this SUV offers proven durability and Lexus quality that\'s built to last .Powered by a 4.6L V8 engine delivering 301 horsepower and 329 lb-ft of torque. Paired with a 6-speed automatic transmission for smooth, responsive driving. Standard full-time 4WD system with a Torsen limited-slip center differential. Body-on-frame construction provides excellent strength for towing and off-road adventures. Towing capacity up to 6,500 lbs, perfect for boats, trailers, or campers. Off-road ready with Crawl Control, Downhill Assist Control, and Hill-Start Assist Control. The Lexus GX 460 delivers premium luxury with thoughtful design touches: Three-row seating with room for up to 7 passengers. Leather-trimmed interior with heated and ventilated front seats. Power-adjustable front seats with memory settings for personalized comfort. Premium infotainment system with 8-inch display, navigation, Bluetooth , USB, and HD Radio. Mark Levinson premium audio system available for true audiophile sound. Tri-zone automatic climate control, keeping all passengers comfortable. Power-folding third-row seats for added cargo versatility.10 airbags including knee, side, and curtain airbags. Rearview camera and parking sensors for confident maneuvering. Advanced safety systems like stability control, traction control, and ABS brakes. Lexus\' reputation for safety and reliability makes this SUV a smart investment. With 137,122 miles, this GX 460 showcases the long-lasting dependability Lexus is known for. These models are sought after for their blend of rugged capability and luxury comfort. Iconic white finish paired with timeless Lexus styling. V8 power, 4WD capability, and luxury all in one SUV. Seating for 7 with flexible cargo space. Lexus quality and durability -- built to go the distance. This 2016 Lexus GX 460 offers the best of both worlds: luxury refinement and serious capability. Don\'t wait -- SUVs of this caliber don\'t stay on the lot for long. Price does not include $0 processing fee

description: One Owner Vehicle!CARFAX One-Owner. Clean CARFAX.AWD, Navigation System/GPS/NAV, Panoramic Roof, Blind Spot Monitors, 24-Way Heated & Cooled Massage Electric Fr Seats, ClearSight Interior Rear-View Mirror, Cold Climate Pack, Convenience Pack, Head-Up Display, Heated front seats, Heated rear seats, Heated Windscreen, Meridian 3D Surround Sound System, Pixel LED Headlights w/Signature DRL, Powered Gesture Tailgate/Boot Lid, Premium Upgrade Interior Pack, Shadow Exterior Pack, Ventilated front seats, Ventilated rear seats, Wheels: 22" Gloss Black.Powertrain & PerformanceType: Plug-in hybrid (gas + electric) with a 3.0 L six-cylinder engine paired with an electric motor (P550e).Electric-only range: ~53 miles on battery-only power (EPA estimate).Combined fuel economy (when battery is depleted): ~21 mpg (city/highway similar).Driving system: Standard all-wheel drive (4WD).Key FiguresTotal seating: 5 passengers.Cargo capacity: ~40.7 cu ft.Curb weight: About 6,025 lbs.Electric motor + gas combo output: Around 543 hp and 406 lb-ft in P550e applications (varies slightly by source/trim).Note: Exact horsepower and torque can vary depending on specific market specs and optional engine packages.Charging & Electric UseThe PHEV can be charged at home on Level 2 chargers and typically offers ~50+ miles of electric range, plenty for many daily commutes.Some owners report typical Level 2 charging takes a few hours for a full charge.What Its Like To DriveOffers a quiet and smooth ride in EV mode with electric-only driving possible for local trips.In hybrid mode, efficiency improves significantly compared with pure gas versions, especially for mixed driving.Some feedback notes hefty weight and handling trade-offs typical for large PHEVs.duPont REGISTRY NewsNotes & TipsLand Rovers Range Rover lineup also includes mild-hybrid and V8 options, the PHEV is the choice if you want electric driving capability + luxe SUV balance.Charging and battery care (like maintaining battery state between ~2080%) is a common topic among owners.Every used vehicle on our lot goes through a strenuous, multi-point inspection before its ever offered for sale because quality and safety aren't just priorities for us, they're part of our heritage. Our factory-trained technicians thoroughly examine all major systems, including the engine, transmission, brakes, suspension, tires, and electrical components, to ensure each vehicle meets our high standards for performance and reliability. We also inspect for signs of prior damage, mechanical issues, and cosmetic wear, inside and out. We believe that every customer deserves to be treated with the same honesty, care, and respect we would offer to our does not meet our strict criteria, its either repaired or replaced before the vehicle reaches the lot. This careful process reflects our commitment to your peace of mind, you deserve a vehicle you can count on.From the moment you walk through our doors or reach out online, our goal is to create a welcoming environment where your needs come first. Whether you're here to explore your next vehicle, schedule service, or simply ask a question, our team is committed to listening, understanding, and guiding you without pressure because building trust matters more than making a sale.

2024 BMW X6 M Competition AWD
One-Owner - Impeccable Service History - Executive Package - Driving Assistance Pro

This high-performance 2024 BMW X6 M blends sports car exhilaration with bold SUV utility powered by a 617-hp 4.4L M TwinPower Turbo V8, paired to an 8-speed sport automatic transmission and BMWs intelligent xDrive all-wheel drive system. Finished in stunning Toronto Red Metallic over Black Extended Merino Leather, this X6 M radiates presence and power.

Factory MSRP: $133,645
Current mileage: 35,950 miles below average for its age

Highly Equipped with Factory Options:
- Executive Package Panoramic Sky Lounge LED roof, front ventilated and massaging seats, soft-close doors, rear side window shades, heated & cooled cupholders, heated front/rear seats
- Driving Assistance Professional Package Active Lane Keeping Assistant, Active Driving Assistant Pro, Traffic Jam Assist, Active Cruise Control with Stop & Go
- 21"/22" Black M Wheels with high-performance tires
- M Compound Brakes with Red Calipers
- Harman Kardon Surround Sound System
- Wireless Apple CarPlay & Android Auto
- Heated Multi-Function Front Seats with Lumbar Support
- SiriusXM with 360L and 1-year Platinum Plan

Originally leased and serviced exclusively through BMW, this X6 M has no accidents, a clean CARFAX, and 9 documented service visits at Jackie Cooper BMW in Oklahoma, including recent maintenance such as oil/filter changes, spark plug replacement, and brake service.

Warranty Coverage:
BMWs original 4-year/50,000-mile warranty is still active with an estimated 17 months or ~20,900 miles remaining. (Confirm exact details with dealership).

With an original MSRP of $133K+, and comparable new models exceeding $140,000 in todays market, this X6 M represents standout value for the performance luxury SUV segment.

Luxury Buying Made Effortless
At Mercedes-Benz of North Olmsted, we're transforming the dealership experience. Our Worry-Free Pricing ensures a hassle-free process no pressure, no games just transparent, market-based pricing from the start, giving you complete confidence while you shop.
We specialize in out-of-town and out-of-state transactions and proudly deliver nationwide. Experience the premier destination for luxury vehicles, competitive pricing, and a team that's dedicated to exceeding your expectations.

The 2025 Ford Expedition Tremor is a commanding presence on the road, blending exceptional capability with refined luxury. This striking SUV boasts a bold, imposing stance and a suite of premium features that elevate the driving experience.

â€¢ Glacier Gray Metallic TriCoat exterior
â€¢ Equipment Group 501A High Package
â€¢ Navigation System
â€¢ 2nd Row Power-Folding Captain's Chairs

Powered by a potent 3.5L V6 engine paired with a responsive 10-speed automatic transmission, the Expedition Tremor delivers confident 4WD performance, whether you're navigating the city streets or exploring the great outdoors. With its impressive towing capacity and spacious, well-appointed interior, this SUV is the perfect companion for your active lifestyle.

Climb inside and you'll be surrounded by premium amenities that cater to your every need. The heated and ventilated leather front captain's chairs provide exceptional comfort, while the expansive Vista Roof fills the cabin with natural light. The advanced infotainment system, featuring a premium B&O sound system, seamlessly integrates your smartphone via Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, keeping you connected and entertained.

Safety is paramount in the Expedition Tremor, with a comprehensive suite of driver-assist technologies that include Blind Spot Monitoring, Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, and Lane Keeping Assist. You can navigate with confidence, knowing that this SUV is equipped to help protect you and your passengers.

Whether you're transporting the family, towing your weekend toys, or embarking on an off-road adventure, the 2025 Ford Expedition Tremor is a versatile and capable SUV that will elevate your driving experience. We invite you to visit our showroom and experience the power, luxury, and innovation that this exceptional vehicle has to offer.

This Lifted 2025 Toyota Sequoia TRD Pro Hybrid features a 2.5-inch Westcott Designs Lift Kit, Four Wheel Alignment, 20-inch Arena A106 Trek Satin Black Wheels, 35X12.50R20 Nitto Ridge Grappler Tires, and Professionally Installed Window Tint with a Lifetime Warranty. Installed by our Lift Tech, Rand. *Modifications are optional and are not included in the advertised price.*

Dominate the road and the trail in our One Owner and Clean Carfax 2025 Toyota Sequoia TRD Pro 4WD in Midnight Black Metallic, a rugged, full-size SUV built with off-road capability, powerful performance, and premium features for bold, family-focused adventures! Motivated by a Twin-TurboCharged 3.4 Liter i-FORCE MAX Hybrid V6 and an Electric Motor delivering a combined 437hp to a 10 Speed Automatic transmission with Multi-Terrain Select. A TRD Pro off-road suspension and an electronic locking rear diff combine for incredible capability, and this Four Wheel Drive SUV returns nearly 22mpg on the highway. Our Sequoia radiates rugged style with a TRD aluminum front skid plate, running boards, premium LED lighting with an LED light bar, and a power sunroof.

Inside our TRD Pro cabin, you'll find upscale details like heated/ventilated SofTex power front seats with exclusive inserts, second-row captain's chairs, a power recline third row, a heated leather TRD steering wheel, tri-zone automatic climate control, and a red TRD start button. Connecting is a breeze with a 14-inch touchscreen, a 12.3-inch driver display, wireless charging, wireless Android Auto/Apple CarPlay, WiFi compatibility, Bluetooth, and JBL audio.

You can confidently explore your world, knowing Toyota supplies adaptive cruise control, a digital rearview mirror, a panoramic view monitor, trailer backup assistance, blind-spot monitoring, automatic braking, lane-departure alert, forward collision warning, and more. Top-shelf amenities like those are just the start for our Sequoia TRD Pro. Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Test Drive Toward Ownership!

Lifted Trucks has built an unmatched reputation over the last two decades for customizing and selling thousands of the highest quality used vehicles in the country. Our inventory is nationally sourced by our certified buyers who cherry-pick only the best-of-the-best of what is available. These vehicles then go through an 82-point inspection process to guarantee quality and safety.

Our lift kits are installed by our own factory-trained technicians who have thousands of hours of experience. The installation is then inspected by a second dedicated quality-control technician before being sent to our state-of-the-art Hunter Engineering laser alignment rack.

Our aftermarket research and development team always matches the best fitting lift kit, shocks, and wheel & tire combinations to each individual vehicle for optimal off-road performance while maintaining an incredibly smooth ride on the street. We never cut any corners on our builds, which is why we only use top-quality name-brand products when building your Truck, SUV or Jeep.

Lifted Trucks has thousands of 5-star reviews and one of the highest rates of repeat customers in the auto industry. Stop by today and experience the difference!

The Bose Centerpoint Premium 14-speaker surround sound system ensures an immersive audio experience, while the wireless phone projection capabilities keep you connected on the go.

The advanced 4-wheel drive system delivers exceptional traction and control, giving you the confidence to conquer any challenge.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like dual front impact airbags, emergency communication system, and advanced driver assistance technologies ensuring your peace of mind behind the wheel.

Vehicle Details
Discover luxury and power with this 2024 Cadillac Escalade 4WD Sport Platinum, now available in Naples, FL. With only 27,958 low miles, this premium full-size SUV pairs a robust 6.2L V8 gasoline engine with four-wheel drive for confident performance on any road. The Sport Platinum trim delivers upscale comfort and advanced technology, making every drive an elevated experience. 2024 Land Rover Defender 130 X Three-Row Luxury, Legendary Capability

The 2024 Land Rover Defender 130 X is where refined luxury meets uncompromising versatility. Powered by a smooth and responsive 3.0L inline-6 with 4WD, this extended-wheelbase Defender is engineered to carry your family and your adventures in first-class comfort.

Designed with families in mind, the Defender 130 offers true three-row seating with a spacious third row, making room for kids, guests, or gear without sacrificing comfort. Up front, 14-Way Climate Electric Memory Seats provide personalized support, while adaptive suspension delivers a composed, confident ride whether you're navigating city streets or heading out of town.

Technology is seamlessly integrated throughout the cabin. The intuitive PIVI Pro Connected Navigation system pairs effortlessly with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, keeping everyone connected and entertained. A power panoramic moonroof floods the interior with natural light, enhancing the open, airy feel for all three rows. The Meridian 400W sound system provides rich, clear audio for every seat in the house.

Finished with bold 20" Gloss Dark Grey Style 5095 wheels and Defender X design elements, this 130 makes a strong, sophisticated statement equally at home at school drop-off or on a weekend escape to Sedona.

3.0L Inline-6 | 4WD

14-Way Climate Electric Memory Front Seats

Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-off cruise control - Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now with hands-off cruise control simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles with minimal steering input from you. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-off cruise control.
  • Super Cruise (3-year subscription) hands-on cruise control with lane change
